{"title":"湖乡春","authors":["申身"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":4,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖乡春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"申身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜浇返青水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖水清清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着岸上拿锨的村姑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映着水边红色的水泵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽上来的返青水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开得浪花一丛丛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着一路春灌曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进解冻的麦垄中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春灌虽是春春灌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年春灌不相同。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去春春灌——辘轳拧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今春春灌——自买了泵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自家买的泵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自家涂上红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成了农家一颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着春在动……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晾渔网"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔网晾在滩头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半网杏影淡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半网阳光柔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风浪中带来的疲劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全从网眼溜走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔舟枕浪头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相伴翻飞两只鸥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光醉了桅杆影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠悠晃晃，晃晃悠悠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看似画一幅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听是歌一首……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孵鸭小曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月牙沉西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁向深夜赠小曲？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缕缕续续，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透出孵鸭房的玻璃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——孵鸭把式大李，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开了三炕活黄菊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出了蛋壳的雏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙着去戏水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孵鸭手艺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻在穷困里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光棍打到四十一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多亏春风送暖来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孵鸭孵成了新女婿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜已深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该休息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽记媳妇娘家去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打个喷嚏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断了小曲……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}